CADE message format

/**
 *                         CADE Message format
 *
 *  +----------------------------------+---------+---------+---------+-----------------+-----------------+-----------------------------------------+
 *  | Protocol                         | Version | Role    | Msg type| ID              | Sequence number | Payloads                                |
 *  +----------------------------------+---------+---------+---------+--+-----------------+-----------------+--------------------------------------+
 *  | 4 octets                         | 1 octet | 1 octet | 1 octet | 2 octets        | 2 octets        | tag length value                        |
 *  +----------------------------------+---------+---------+---------+-----------------+-----------------+-----------------------------------------+
 *  | C  A  D  E                       | 1       | PLAYER  | HELLO   | 123             | 1               |                                         |
 *  +----------------------------------+---------+---------+---------+-----------------+-----------------+-----------------------------------------+
 *
 */
